        {
            "title": "MMTC Limited Reports Earnings Results for the Second Quarter and Six Months Ended September 30, 2025",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\">\n        \n                    MMTC Limited reported earnings results for the second quarter and six months ended September 30, 2025. For the second quarter, the company reported sales was INR 11 million compared to INR 15.6 million a year ago. Revenue was INR 384.7 million compared to INR 445.8 million a year ago. Net income was INR 1,708.1 million compared to INR 480.5 million a year ago. Basic earnings per share from continuing operations was INR 1.14 compared to INR 0.32 a year ago. Diluted earnings per share from continuing operations was INR 1.14 compared to INR 32 a year ago.<br/>\rFor the six months, sales was INR 24.6 million compared to INR 22.1 million a year ago. Revenue was INR 1,100.3 million compared to INR 1,833.3 million a year ago. Net income was INR 2,150.7 million compared to INR 807.4 million a year ago. Basic earnings per share from continuing operations was INR 1.43 compared to INR 0.54 a year ago. Diluted earnings per share from continuing operations was INR 1.43 compared to INR 0.54 a year ago.\n    \n    </div>",
            "link": "https://hk.marketscreener.com/news/mmtc-limited-reports-earnings-results-for-the-second-quarter-and-six-months-ended-september-30-2025-ce7d5fddda8cf72c",
